ccessible=true. Tests can use Vertx.vertx(), WebClient.create(...), and a loopback HttpServer; no external service is needed.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"OAuth2WebClient is part of the artifact API but depends on optional io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2; avoid OAuth2-specific tests unless that optional dependency is intentionally added.\",\n    \"The unsafe-access properties are motivated by Java 25/native-image current-defaults with Netty 4.2.x; local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a5dfdbf77ba12a8016a3f69b37ef88195a90fa054733379d8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1753, "output": 545, "cacheRead": 32256, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34554, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782540712525, "responseId": "resp_0a5dfdbf77ba12a8016a3f69a905888195b94ec47ed1d20f5a"}}
